cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper focuses on computer vision and machine learning techniques for gait recognition, which suggests that it belongs to the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of multiple modalities and the comparison of different CNN architectures also suggest that it could belong to the multimedia (cs.MM), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-categories.
